## 快速示例

创建一个带 SpriteRenderer 的 GameObject：

```json
{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "jobId": "example_001",
  "projectWriteRoot": "Assets/AutoGen",
  "commands": [
    {
      "cmd": "CreateGameObject",
      "args": { "name": "MySprite", "ensure": true },
      "out": { "go": "$obj" }
    },
    {
      "cmd": "AddComponent",
      "args": {
        "target": { "ref": "$obj" },
        "type": "UnityEngine.SpriteRenderer"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

当用户请求 Unity 相关的创建、修改操作时，请查阅 `.agent/skills/` 中的详细文档来构建和执行 Job。
